CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 25, 2010

[Cite as 01/25/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-187.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2009-2022. In re Application of Columbus S. Power Company.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 08-917-EL-SSO. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the motion for leave to intervene as appellees of Columbus Southern Power Company and Ohio Power Company,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
